OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FThousands of people have been ordered
OL,7,Fto evacuate their homes in southern
OL,8,FCalifornia as a wind-driven wildfire
OL,9,Fspreads dangerously fast.
OL,11,FAt least one home has been damaged in
OL,12,Fthe blaze, which was first reported at
OL,13,F10am in the hills above Simi Valley,
OL,14,Fabout 30 miles northwest of Los
OL,15,FAngeles, the Ventura County Fire
OL,16,FDepartment said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
