OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FBy mid-afternoon it had consumed more
OL,7,Fthan 500 acres of dry brush, causing
OL,8,Fevacuation orders to be issued for
OL,9,Fseveral neighbourhoods in Simi Valley,
OL,10,Fwhere more than 125,000 people live.
OL,12,FWatch Duty, a real-time fire alert
OL,13,Fservice, put the blaze's perimeter at
OL,14,Fmore than 1,360 acres late on Monday
OL,15,Fevening, local time.
OL,17,FNamed Sandy Fire, due to its location
OL,18,Fby Sandy Avenue, the flames were
OL,19,Fpushed by winds that surpassed 30mph,
OL,20,Ffire department spokesperson Scott
OL,21,FDettorre said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
