OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FThese subsided during the afternoon
OL,7,Fand were expected to calm down further
OL,8,Fby the evening, Dettorre said on
OL,9,FMonday.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe cause of the fire is under
OL,17,Finvestigation.
