OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FAn evacuation point and two animal
OL,7,Fshelters have been established by the
OL,8,FCalifornia Department of Forestry and
OL,9,FFire Protection.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, firefighters are also
OL,12,Fbattling a 15-square-mile blaze on
OL,13,FSanta Rosa Island, the second-largest
OL,14,Fof the Channel Islands off the
OL,15,FSouthern California coast, in which an
OL,16,Festimated 14,600 acres have burned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
