OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FThe fire, first reported on May 15,
OL,7,Fhas destroyed two historic buildings
OL,8,Fand an equipment shed, and forced the
OL,9,Fevacuation of multiple National Park
OL,10,FService employees.
OL,12,FOfficials have called it the largest
OL,13,Ffire to ever be recorded on the island.
OL,15,FThe land is a popular destination for
OL,16,Fcamping and hiking, and home to
OL,17,Fseveral rare species and plants, such
OL,18,Fas island foxes, as well as spotted
OL,19,Fskunks and elephant seals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
