OL,3,CRaging wildfires near Los Angeles
OL,4,Cforce thousands to evacuate their homes
OL,6,FWindy conditions initially made it
OL,7,Fdifficult for firefighters to reach
OL,8,Fthe blaze, a fire information officer
OL,9,Ftold reporters.
